column5: Hi all, I do the odd guiding gig at Wabigoon Lake Outfitters here on beautiful Wabigoon Lake, always fun going out with repeat customers, and the walleye did not disappoint, caught well over 80 for the afternoon with plenty of slots and overs, the kid was a slip bobber wizard.
Great guiding job, They will not forget this trip especially the little Guy. Keep up the good work.
